'''Shell One''' was the innermost of [[the Shells]], the many shells formed by the concentric spheres surrounding [[Hollowtown]] in [[Centerpoint Station]]. Shell One bordered Hollowtown and was connected by small airlocks through which [[Turbolift/Legends|turbovators]] were allowed to pass. There was a small air pressure differential of eight percent between the two areas. Shell One and the outer layers were spared the devastation that Hollowtown experienced when the [[Glowpoint]] flared during the [[Corellian Crisis|First Corellian Insurrection]].

